{"tid":1665292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果唔得閒出去遊行或發夢嘅手足入一入黎！！！","createTime":"2019-10-20T13:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T14:57:51.000Z","uid":4396,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"560ff3e264e97c79155a3c48d9bd5d9326c20b0f","tid":1665292,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:58:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家有上連登都知每一次有活動個陣啲五毛分化畜牲就會出黎搞搞陣，我建議唔得閒或人不在香港嘅手足將呢啲畜牲嘅會員名記低，然後整一個list，再開個post長期置及更新，以便手足辨別分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然手足對呢場革命有任何要求或建議都可以提出，但切記唔好再以任何指責或分化嘅言論黎提出，以後再見有呢啲言論一概視為分化撚處理<br />\n<br />\n謹記：不完美，可接受，有待改善！和勇一家，香港同心，不指責，不分化。多啲包容，多啲鼓勵。<br />\n<br />\n只要我地團結一致，萬眾一心，無野可以阻擋我地前進</span>"},{"pid":"c6f9af4bbbb68fd6890f3df4d651f8cdde2b6cc0","tid":1665292,"uid":150742,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:59:26.000Z","msg":"可以！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffc348f47f72fb80132ae62740e81e6f8ee6f74","tid":1665292,"uid":4396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f02500e1fad7f8ba2976775c257472015f4673c","tid":1665292,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6f9af4bbbb68fd6890f3df4d651f8cdde2b6cc0","tid":1665292,"uid":150742,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:59:26.000Z","msg":"可以！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7192b7330702a679acf27179a009572c16387bae","tid":16652